{
  "texts": [
    "We also provide a series of blueprint tools that can help instructors create prompts for their students that instructors can then test and share.",
    "The prompts in this paper, along with their variations, generally work for all \"GPT-4 class\" models foot_0.",
    "At the time of this writing there are multiple GPT-4 class models available including GPT-4, Google's Gemini 1.5, and Anthropic's Claude 3 Opus.",
    "The first open source GPT-4 class models are expected in the summer of 2024.",
    "In every exercise, we leverage the core capabilities of these models, capabilities that open up new possibilities for teaching and learning including: interactivity, personalization, and a capacity to adapt and improvise."
  ]
}